commits.author: broustant
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Gets the elevation associated to the provided query. *

* By contract and by design, only one elevation may be associated * to a given query (this can be safely verified by an assertion). * * @param queryString The query string (not {@link #analyzeQuery(String) analyzed} yet, * this {@link ElevationProvider} is in charge of analyzing it). * @return The elevation associated with the query; or null if none. */ Elevation getElevationForQuery(String queryString);
